    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 4. Comprehensive Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification across all model inputs demonstrates that aleatory variability in hemolysis index predictions remains within the 20% acceptance band. The relative hemolysis index criterion (RH < 1) is satisfied across all five operating points with adequate margin. The credibility evidence is sufficient to support the regulatory decision for this Class II CPB device.",
